text: Idyash () is a rural locality (a village) in Utyagulovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 613 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 71 km from Isyangulovo, 6 km from Utyagulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Idyash
